law.history: Repealed 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 385, sec. 50, effective July 1, 1982. -- Amended 1954 Ky. Acts ch. 112, sec. 2, effective June 17, 1954. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 3145.
